<plot>Mohanlal plays a Brahmin priest who is falsely accused of theft and forced to leave his village in Kerala. He moves to Bombay where he gets drawn into the underworld through an ageing don Kareem (Goga Kapoor). Some interesting comment initially on Brahmin priesthood in Kerala, but halfway through the film goes haywire. Beware of a completely unnecessary added plot in the last half hour.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?046944</url></doc>
